descript.abstract: This dataset represents the major cities and towns in Mexico. This dataset is from the updated version of the Mexico dataset in ESRI Data and Maps CDs.
descript.purpose: This dataset is used to create the MexicoPopulationDensity.mxd map document.
descript.supplinf: This dataset is in Shapefile format, in geographic coordinates (latitude-longitude).
